headline: Annual Square Research Indicates Year of Experimentation and Customer Focus for Restaurants to Combat Economic Headwinds
summary: Square’s fifth annual report finds that global consumer businesses, including beauty and retail, plan to invest in new automation and loyalty programs in 2025...
